Let's see...

973
01:12:53.225 --> 01:12:55.477
Get up, miss.

974
01:12:57.521 --> 01:13:00.232
I'd give her 30 more drops.

975
01:13:06.280 --> 01:13:08.532
Your antics made
everyone uncomfortable.


976
01:13:08.657 --> 01:13:12.494
- I made everyone uncomfortable ?
- Why are you taking the kids away ?


977
01:13:12.661 --> 01:13:14.746
I'll explain it to you later.

978
01:13:14.913 --> 01:13:17.040
- Bye, kids.
- Say bye to dad.


979
01:13:17.249 --> 01:13:19.251
See you soon.

980
01:13:26.258 --> 01:13:28.886
Is it just the two of us ?

981
01:13:30.053 --> 01:13:32.264
Why did you let her leave ?

982
01:13:32.389 --> 01:13:35.809
She's sweet, she loves you,
she's good for you.


983
01:13:36.518 --> 01:13:40.689
I realize she bores you
but I'm sure she has good points.


984
01:13:40.814 --> 01:13:44.067
She doesn't bore me,
why do you think that ?


985
01:13:44.318 --> 01:13:47.321
Don't be so disparaging
of the poor thing.


986
01:13:47.446 --> 01:13:50.574
- I love her, you know.
- Of course.


987
01:13:51.074 --> 01:13:53.076
She's not like you

988
01:13:53.285 --> 01:13:56.580
and that orangutan jailbird
you cheated on me with.


989
01:13:56.705 --> 01:13:59.708
You even forced me to represent him.

990
01:14:11.303 --> 01:14:13.305
You're beautiful.

991
01:14:13.430 --> 01:14:16.975
I bought it in a cheap store
but it's rather cute.


992
01:14:17.184 --> 01:14:21.355
- Tell me, have you seen him again ?
- Stop it.


993
01:14:21.730 --> 01:14:24.358
I was afraid
you ran away to go see him.


994
01:14:24.566 --> 01:14:27.611
You're so jealous !

995
01:14:29.613 --> 01:14:32.115
Tomorrow I'll take you back
to the clinic


996
01:14:32.324 --> 01:14:34.701
and I'll have myself admitted too.

997
01:14:34.868 --> 01:14:38.497
Yes, in the special ward
for clingy types.


998
01:14:39.206 --> 01:14:41.959
Clingy.

999
01:14:55.973 --> 01:14:58.016
"Donatella Morelli - son"

1000
01:15:01.269 --> 01:15:03.981
"Rescued while trying to kill herself
and 8-month-old son"


1001
01:15:07.025 --> 01:15:09.111
"She wanted to kill her son"

1002
01:15:11.154 --> 01:15:14.157
"The boy swallowed a lot of water
and couldn't breathe".


1003
01:15:15.784 --> 01:15:17.160
"Enraged crowd:
she wanted to kill her son"


1004
01:15:17.369 --> 01:15:19.871
"She has a past of drug use
and mental health issues"


1005
01:15:21.498 --> 01:15:23.375
"Attempted infanticide"

1006
01:15:55.157 --> 01:15:58.660
- Are you coming back ?
- God no, this place is a drag.


1007
01:15:58.827 --> 01:16:01.204
I'm sorry you're leaving.

1008
01:16:01.413 --> 01:16:03.457
Goodbye.

1009
01:16:06.960 --> 01:16:10.422
No need... I'm a big girl now,
goodbye.


1010
01:16:10.714 --> 01:16:14.176
- Where to ?
- Away from here for now.


1011
01:16:14.301 --> 01:16:17.554
"Was Donatella Morelli
institutionalized ? Attorney Aitiani"


1012
01:16:19.723 --> 01:16:21.933
- Mind if I smoke ?
- It's illegal.


1013
01:16:22.100 --> 01:16:24.186
Thanks, so kind.

1014
01:16:25.062 --> 01:16:28.065
How much would it cost
to go to Mantua ?


1015
01:16:28.231 --> 01:16:31.735
At least 500 euros, ma'am.

1016
01:16:31.860 --> 01:16:33.612
Make it 1,000...

1017
01:16:33.820 --> 01:16:36.364
- Are you married ?
- With all due respect, yes.


1018
01:16:36.990 --> 01:16:39.951
Let your wife know you're mine today.

1019
01:16:41.995 --> 01:16:45.457
- How long has she been here ?
- Since this morning.


1020
01:16:47.751 --> 01:16:49.753
Donatella...

1021
01:16:50.504 --> 01:16:52.631
Shall we get up ?

1022
01:16:53.215 --> 01:16:55.592
Come on.

1023
01:16:56.134 --> 01:16:57.636
Did she eat?

1024
01:16:57.844 --> 01:17:00.722
Dunno, I can't spoon-feed them all !

1025
01:17:00.889 --> 01:17:03.642
- Did she take her meds ?
- She's a greedy one...


1026
01:17:04.101 --> 01:17:07.479
She wants to up the doses,
says it's not enough.


1027
01:17:11.149 --> 01:17:13.360
What would you like ?

1028
01:17:14.528 --> 01:17:16.113
Electroshock. <i>..</i>

1029
01:17:17.030 --> 01:17:18.657
please.

1030
01:17:19.866 --> 01:17:23.787
She did a few rounds in Pisa

1031
01:17:23.995 --> 01:17:27.290
Why keep her here ?
Let's send her back there.


1032
01:17:27.666 --> 01:17:30.293
Go get me her chart.

1033
01:17:36.508 --> 01:17:38.802
Unlock her room for me.

1034
01:17:42.764 --> 01:17:45.308
I'll help you.

1035
01:17:53.692 --> 01:17:55.318
Thank you.

1036
01:17:58.321 --> 01:17:59.948
You're welcome.

1037
01:18:00.532 --> 01:18:02.534
- Thank you.
- You're welcome.


1038
01:18:02.701 --> 01:18:05.912
Come on, you can do it.

1039
01:18:08.957 --> 01:18:11.168
- Wait here.
- Okay.


1040
01:18:16.548 --> 01:18:21.469
Good morning, I just need 5 minutes
to see a relative.


1041
01:18:21.595 --> 01:18:25.098
- Sorry, I can't allow that.
- I'll be quick, really.


1042
01:18:25.932 --> 01:18:29.227
Check with the office,
I sent an email...


1043
01:18:29.352 --> 01:18:30.979
I can't allow that.

1044
01:18:31.188 --> 01:18:32.731
Are you a broken record ?

1045
01:18:32.939 --> 01:18:36.318
- I can't allow that, please leave.
- So rude I


1046
01:18:37.611 --> 01:18:40.739
I'd like to speak to
Donatella Morelli, please.


1047
01:18:42.866 --> 01:18:45.368
Yes, she's a patient of yours.

1048
01:18:45.577 --> 01:18:47.579
It's boiling.

1049
01:18:48.496 --> 01:18:50.081
I'm a relative...

1050
01:18:50.498 --> 01:18:52.334
<i>Yes.</i>

1051
01:18:53.084 --> 01:18:56.338
Her mother, Lucia...

1052
01:18:56.630 --> 01:18:59.591
I mean Luciana,
Lucia's my nickname.


1053
01:18:59.758 --> 01:19:01.468
Luciana Morelli.

1054
01:19:01.718 --> 01:19:03.845
"Juvenile court
finalizes the adoption by


1055
01:19:04.012 --> 01:19:07.641
Mauro and Alessandra Bonanno
of Via Bonamico 52, Viareggio".


1056
01:19:07.766 --> 01:19:11.102
It's not possible ?
What if I call back later ?


1057
01:19:11.978 --> 01:19:14.397
Perfect, thanks. Goodbye.

1058
01:19:15.398 --> 01:19:17.234
Excuse me,

1059
01:19:17.400 --> 01:19:20.528
I've changed my mind,
a cappuccino instead of tea.


1060
01:19:21.112 --> 01:19:23.657
- With lots of foam.
- Lots of foam.


1061
01:19:27.160 --> 01:19:29.412
No, leave the cookies.

1062
01:19:30.413 --> 01:19:32.374
Hi, Snuggles.

1063
01:19:33.667 --> 01:19:35.794
No, it's nothing.

1064
01:19:35.919 --> 01:19:38.672
I only gave you 40 drops.

1065
01:19:39.047 --> 01:19:40.924
You seemed stressed,

1066
01:19:41.049 --> 01:19:44.386
I thought you could use a good rest...

1067
01:19:46.388 --> 01:19:48.765
I'll bring it all back, I'm no thief!

1068
01:20:07.409 --> 01:20:09.411
This is for you.

1069
01:20:10.287 --> 01:20:12.706
You didn't get it from me, understand ?

1070
01:20:12.831 --> 01:20:16.293
Don't get me in trouble, hear me ?

1071
01:20:34.561 --> 01:20:37.314
"I know everything.
You have to see your son !


1072
01:20:37.480 --> 01:20:40.859
I'll take you to him !
Meet me at Capannori, Lucca."


1073
01:20:46.740 --> 01:20:49.617
"it's not your style
but it's worth 35,000 euros !


1074
01:20:49.743 --> 01:20:53.621
If you want to get out of there,
do it Italian-style. Hugs"


1075
01:21:05.759 --> 01:21:07.469
She's a nutcase.

1076
01:21:08.345 --> 01:21:10.138
She's a nutcase.

1077
01:21:11.014 --> 01:21:12.766
A real nutcase !

1078
01:21:30.533 --> 01:21:34.287
- Who is <i>it ?</i>
- Renato, honey, can I come in ?


1079
01:21:35.747 --> 01:21:39.876
Will you open up ? It's important,
I have something for you.


1080
01:21:42.545 --> 01:21:44.172
- Take this !
- But why !?


1081
01:21:44.297 --> 01:21:47.634
Stop it !
Why are you doing this, honey ?


1082
01:21:47.801 --> 01:21:51.554
Your faggy husband
swore he'd spoken to the judge


1083
01:21:52.013 --> 01:21:53.932
but I found out it wasn't true.

1084
01:21:54.140 --> 01:21:57.811
How much longer do I have to stay
locked up in this shithole ?


1085
01:21:58.269 --> 01:22:00.021
I have cash, for you !

1086
01:22:00.271 --> 01:22:02.148
I know you need <i>it...</i>

1087
01:22:02.315 --> 01:22:04.317
- Everything okay, ma'am ?
- Yes...


1088
01:22:04.442 --> 01:22:06.694
Don't worry, leave me alone.

1089
01:22:07.779 --> 01:22:09.572
Let me come up for a minute.

1090
01:22:09.781 --> 01:22:12.659
Renato said to give it to me.

1091
01:22:16.162 --> 01:22:18.206
Give it to her ?

1092
01:22:18.331 --> 01:22:21.334
- Got a problem with that ?
- No...


1093
01:22:21.459 --> 01:22:25.046
Are you in a steady relationship ?

1094
01:22:25.213 --> 01:22:27.090
- Is it serious ?
- The money...


1095
01:22:28.425 --> 01:22:30.468
- Here's the money.
- Yes.


1096
01:22:31.845 --> 01:22:35.473
- I can give you these too...
- I can't allow this.


1097
01:22:35.807 --> 01:22:38.977
I know it's not my business,
but we should get out of here.


1098
01:22:39.477 --> 01:22:41.104
Who the fuck are you ?!

1099
01:22:41.229 --> 01:22:43.815
You can't take advantage
of her like this.


1100
01:22:44.107 --> 01:22:45.984
Geppetto, I'll find you !

1101
01:22:46.192 --> 01:22:49.988
- I was going to pay you anyway.
- That's not it, let's just go.


1102
01:22:50.113 --> 01:22:53.074
You're a psychopath,
you ruined my life !


1103
01:22:53.241 --> 01:22:55.368
- Love...
- Love, my ass !


1104
01:22:55.493 --> 01:22:58.955
Don't use vulgar gestures
like that with me.


1105
01:23:00.206 --> 01:23:05.086
Drag in everyone
who was here on duty last night !


1106
01:23:05.253 --> 01:23:07.380
And let me know.

1107
01:23:08.465 --> 01:23:09.507
Nothing.

1108
01:23:22.270 --> 01:23:24.272
Thanks.

1109
01:23:35.116 --> 01:23:39.287
Excuse me, I'm looking for Beatrice.
Moreschini Valdirana...


1110
01:23:39.537 --> 01:23:41.748
Dunno, go ask them.

1111
01:23:41.873 --> 01:23:43.917
- Thanks.
- You're welcome.


1112
01:23:52.008 --> 01:23:54.177
Are you looking for Beatrice ?

1113
01:23:54.385 --> 01:23:57.055
Yes, she and I are friends.

1114
01:23:57.555 --> 01:24:00.266
- I'm her mom, come with me.
- How nice.


1115
01:24:00.433 --> 01:24:04.020
That nutcase has parked herself
in the guesthouse


1116
01:24:04.187 --> 01:24:06.689
and we can't get her out.

1117
01:24:06.898 --> 01:24:10.944
They want to shoot in there,
the set designers need to prep it.


1118
01:24:11.069 --> 01:24:14.322
No worries,
she and I will get out of your hair.


1119
01:24:14.447 --> 01:24:16.908
Good, go very far away.

1120
01:24:17.325 --> 01:24:20.036
Is this Beatrice's house ?

1121
01:24:20.203 --> 01:24:23.540
In her dreams, this is my house !

1122
01:24:24.457 --> 01:24:28.586
You can't imagine the havoc
she has wreaked in our lives.


1123
01:24:28.795 --> 01:24:30.922
She's an egoistic liar.

1124
01:24:31.047 --> 01:24:35.093
She's been deceiving people
her whole life, starting with us


1125
01:24:35.301 --> 01:24:39.097
until she came across
an even bigger cheat.


1126
01:24:39.305 --> 01:24:43.726
That unspeakable creature,
Renato Corsi !


1127
01:24:45.103 --> 01:24:47.313
A real imposter

1128
01:24:47.480 --> 01:24:50.316
who sold nonexistent property.

1129
01:24:50.733 --> 01:24:52.735
And what did that dummy do ?

1130
01:24:52.986 --> 01:24:57.365
She lost her head for him,
and he brought us to our knees !


1131
01:24:57.490 --> 01:25:02.453
She signed anything
that crook put under her nose.


1132
01:25:02.620 --> 01:25:06.708
She got hit with two counts
of bankruptcy fraud


1133
01:25:07.500 --> 01:25:11.963
and the family patrimony was drained
from all the fines.


1134
01:25:12.755 --> 01:25:17.385
We've been reduced to renting out
our home for Italian movies...


1135
01:25:17.510 --> 01:25:19.262
Can you imagine ?

1136
01:25:19.887 --> 01:25:24.517
And every time she comes back here,
repentant and dejected.


1137
01:25:25.351 --> 01:25:28.896
But enough's enough,
I have no pity left for her.


1138
01:25:29.022 --> 01:25:31.774
She should kill herself
and put an end to it.


1139
01:25:34.235 --> 01:25:36.279
<i>Go</i> in <i>there...</i>

1140
01:25:36.487 --> 01:25:40.617
and tell her to get a move on.
Goodbye.


1141
01:25:57.550 --> 01:26:00.011
I made it, I'm here !

1142
01:26:01.054 --> 01:26:03.681
- It's you ?
- Yes, it's me.


1143
01:26:03.806 --> 01:26:07.018
I ran away, can you believe it?

1144
01:26:07.185 --> 01:26:09.187
Can you believe it?

1145
01:26:09.312 --> 01:26:13.024
- I'm happy you've come.
- I've missed you.


1146
01:26:13.191 --> 01:26:16.027
I have a fever, I'm all achy.

1147
01:26:16.152 --> 01:26:18.571
Nonsense, sit up.

1148
01:26:20.031 --> 01:26:22.450
- My sciatica's acting up.
- You'll be fine.


1149
01:26:22.659 --> 01:26:24.827
It happens every time I come here.

1150
01:26:26.663 --> 01:26:30.458
- No, these are slippers...
- It's a zoo out there.


1151
01:26:30.833 --> 01:26:32.585
It's cool.

1152
01:26:32.794 --> 01:26:39.050
They're such clods... they put
fake camellias on the rose bushes.


1153
01:26:39.217 --> 01:26:41.052
Where's the other shoe ?

1154
01:26:41.219 --> 01:26:44.430
But those vintage cars are lovely.

1155
01:26:44.597 --> 01:26:46.724
Let's go see him.

1156
01:26:47.100 --> 01:26:48.226
Who ?

1157
01:26:49.560 --> 01:26:52.814
What do you mean ? Him.
You said you'd take me to him !


1158
01:26:52.980 --> 01:26:55.817
You wrote it here,
don't you remember ?


1159
01:26:55.983 --> 01:26:57.944
Are you blind ? Read it !

1160
01:26:58.611 --> 01:26:59.946
Come on !

1161
01:27:00.738 --> 01:27:04.117
Maraschini Mangiarana,
move it or I'll beat you senseless.


1162
01:27:04.242 --> 01:27:06.244
Has anyone ever beat you senseless ?

1163
01:27:06.369 --> 01:27:08.955
Well, I will if you don't move it.

1164
01:27:09.080 --> 01:27:12.375
Move it, ladies,
are you in scene 38 ?


1165
01:27:12.583 --> 01:27:14.877
Go to wardrobe, asap !

1166
01:27:15.086 --> 01:27:17.880
Wardrobe is this way, come on !

1167
01:27:18.464 --> 01:27:21.759
- Aren't you an extra ?
- She's a cutie.


1168
01:27:21.884 --> 01:27:24.595
Francesca wants to start
with the Lancia shot.


1169
01:27:24.762 --> 01:27:26.764
- Got a license ?
- Yes.


1170
01:27:26.973 --> 01:27:30.893
- We're actually leaving.
- We're in the Lancia Appia scene.


1171
01:27:31.102 --> 01:27:33.479
- Then go to wardrobe.
- We're together.


1172
01:27:33.646 --> 01:27:35.732
Shut up, dummy.

1173
01:27:35.898 --> 01:27:39.736
I'm thrilled we'll be in a cabriolet,
I adore cabriolets !


1174
01:27:41.529 --> 01:27:43.531
Are you in scene 38 too ?

1175
01:27:43.990 --> 01:27:47.618
When we say "action",
start the car and drive to the gate.


1176
01:27:47.785 --> 01:27:50.246
<i>Put her wig on, please.</i>

1177
01:27:50.413 --> 01:27:53.249
When we say "cut",
back it up to here.


1178
01:27:53.416 --> 01:27:56.002
Quick, before we lose light.
Clapperboard !


1179
01:27:56.169 --> 01:27:58.796
Easy on the gas,
this thing really flies.


1180
01:27:59.005 --> 01:28:01.924
Silence please. Ready ?
Camera !


1181
01:28:03.176 --> 01:28:05.762
- Rolling !
- Scene 38 take one !


1182
01:28:08.681 --> 01:28:11.809
- What's that idiot doing now ?
- Making movies.


1183
01:28:12.310 --> 01:28:14.312
She's no good.

1184
01:28:14.437 --> 01:28:15.563
Action !

1185
01:28:16.939 --> 01:28:18.816
You're a bunch of Fascists !

1186
01:28:19.025 --> 01:28:22.153
- Elsa, you chased them all away.
- I'll drive this time.


1187
01:28:23.404 --> 01:28:26.532
- Cut !
- Sorry, my bad.


1188
01:28:29.035 --> 01:28:30.787
"Go!
- Stop!


1189
01:28:32.705 --> 01:28:34.582
Stop !

1190
01:29:09.242 --> 01:29:11.744
What's going on ?

1191
01:29:12.245 --> 01:29:14.872
What's going on ?

1192
01:29:15.081 --> 01:29:17.708
<i>Don't know, hold on...</i>

1193
01:29:18.000 --> 01:29:19.836
Hold on !

1194
01:29:20.002 --> 01:29:22.880
We're out of gas, it's no big deal.

1195
01:29:23.256 --> 01:29:24.882
Come along.

1196
01:29:25.508 --> 01:29:28.845
- Down this street.
- Where ?


1197
01:29:29.262 --> 01:29:30.596
You can't stop here.

1198
01:29:30.763 --> 01:29:33.391
Be right back, we have something
important to do.


1199
01:29:33.599 --> 01:29:35.017
Are you crazy ?

1200
01:29:35.142 --> 01:29:38.271
According to some evaluations, yes !

1201
01:29:38.729 --> 01:29:40.147
Come on.

1202
01:29:49.866 --> 01:29:51.492
I'll get it.

1203
01:30:01.168 --> 01:30:03.546
- Mr. Bonanno ?
- Yes.


1204
01:30:04.881 --> 01:30:07.174
Hello, may I have a word ?

1205
01:30:09.135 --> 01:30:12.889
Sorry for disturbing you,
but I believe the time has come


1206
01:30:13.055 --> 01:30:15.558
to face an important aspect
of Elia's life.


1207
01:30:15.683 --> 01:30:20.187
- Our son ? And who are you ?
- I'll explain everything.


1208
01:30:20.396 --> 01:30:25.943
I feel Elia should meet his mother
and hear her side of the story.


1209
01:30:26.402 --> 01:30:29.447
His mother is here, inside the house.

1210
01:30:29.697 --> 01:30:33.075
- Is this about Donatella Morelli ?
- Yes.


1211
01:30:33.284 --> 01:30:38.331
Social services called this morning
to tell us she escaped.


1212
01:30:39.206 --> 01:30:41.584
Escaped... that's a bit much.

1213
01:30:42.084 --> 01:30:45.963
Are you in contact with Ms. Morelli,
where is she ?


1214
01:30:46.172 --> 01:30:48.591
I'm just trying to help out.

1215
01:30:48.799 --> 01:30:52.094
You should listen to me
for the good of your son.


1216
01:30:52.303 --> 01:30:55.598
I don't understand,
are you a psychologist?


1217
01:30:55.806 --> 01:30:59.226
I'm much more than that. Never mind...

1218
01:30:59.435 --> 01:31:02.355
May I have a word
with you as well ?

1219
01:31:09.862 --> 01:31:13.950
Do you realize
you may be committing a crime ?


1220
01:31:14.116 --> 01:31:15.242
Aiding and abetting.

1221
01:31:15.826 --> 01:31:17.745
Know where she is ?

1222
01:31:17.954 --> 01:31:20.998
If so,
you should inform the authorities.


1223
01:31:22.500 --> 01:31:25.503
You have the wrong idea about her.

1224
01:31:25.628 --> 01:31:30.591
I realize she can come across
as someone who's shady,


1225
01:31:30.758 --> 01:31:33.594
crude, boorish, ignorant,

1226
01:31:33.761 --> 01:31:36.764
primitive, almost beast-like
at first glance...


1227
01:31:36.973 --> 01:31:38.766
But she's not.

1228
01:31:38.975 --> 01:31:42.228
She's someone who is good,

1229
01:31:42.395 --> 01:31:45.147
humble, loyal, generous,

1230
01:31:46.273 --> 01:31:48.609
very romantic.

1231
01:31:48.776 --> 01:31:52.905
She is fragile because
her heart is literally broken.


1232
01:31:53.155 --> 01:31:56.659
And since the accident,
her life has been agony.


1233
01:31:56.867 --> 01:31:59.370
- Accident ?
- If you can call it that...


1234
01:31:59.537 --> 01:32:03.541
Let's be honest,
the law is on your side.


1235
01:32:03.749 --> 01:32:05.626
And if you so decide,

1236
01:32:05.793 --> 01:32:09.130
you can impede Donatella
from seeing Elia until he turns 18.


1237
01:32:09.296 --> 01:32:13.426
You might not know, but
these encounters did already occur,


1238
01:32:13.801 --> 01:32:15.928
for three years leading up
to the adoption.


1239
01:32:16.137 --> 01:32:17.680
Yes, of course.

1240
01:32:17.805 --> 01:32:20.641
In a municipal office,

1241
01:32:20.808 --> 01:32:22.810
in a room with two chairs,

1242
01:32:22.935 --> 01:32:26.022
under the scrutiny of psychologists
and social workers.


1243
01:32:26.897 --> 01:32:29.650
We realize it wasn't
the best of environments...


1244
01:32:30.151 --> 01:32:33.654
Yes, but Morelli violated the rules
every single time.


1245
01:32:33.821 --> 01:32:35.823
Because she tried to give him a kiss,
to caress him...


1246
01:32:36.032 --> 01:32:38.451
After the adoption became official,
she caused a fiasco.


1247
01:32:38.659 --> 01:32:42.204
Fiasco ? She just went into his class
to get a look at him,


1248
01:32:42.455 --> 01:32:44.290
she hadn't seen him in <i>2</i> years.

1249
01:32:44.457 --> 01:32:47.209
They assumed she wanted to kidnap him.

1250
01:32:47.460 --> 01:32:50.463
But this upsets Elia too much.

1251
01:32:50.671 --> 01:32:53.215
You know, when we got him

1252
01:32:53.424 --> 01:32:56.343
he couldn't stand up, couldn't sit still...

1253
01:33:18.866 --> 01:33:22.620
Elia, Giada, come eat,
I made fritters.


1254
01:33:23.120 --> 01:33:25.873
Then off to bed,
we're going to the beach early.


1255
01:33:33.964 --> 01:33:35.382
What did they say ?

1256
01:33:35.591 --> 01:33:39.011
We spoke for 30 minutes,
they seem like reasonable folks.


1257
01:33:39.220 --> 01:33:40.513
Can I see him ?

1258
01:33:40.638 --> 01:33:43.224
The wife has a different
Tuscan accent though,


1259
01:33:43.390 --> 01:33:46.852
perhaps from Grosseto or Maremma.

1260
01:33:47.019 --> 01:33:49.146
Can I see him or not?

1261
01:33:49.355 --> 01:33:50.773
No.

1262
01:33:50.898 --> 01:33:54.652
- What did you say for 30 minutes ?!
- Calm down.


1263
01:33:54.860 --> 01:33:59.281
There's a chance that
they'll think it over and contact me.


1264
01:34:00.157 --> 01:34:02.993
Contacts are important in life.

1265
01:34:03.160 --> 01:34:07.665
Now let's find some gas
and go back to the car.


1266
01:34:10.251 --> 01:34:13.754
On second thought, 
I'll call Pierluigi.

1267
01:34:14.380 --> 01:34:16.423
I'll have him come get us.

1268
01:34:16.549 --> 01:34:19.176
So you can finally meet him !

1269
01:34:19.385 --> 01:34:21.303
How does this work ?

1270
01:34:21.512 --> 01:34:23.681
You can ask for legal advice...

1271
01:34:23.889 --> 01:34:26.642
he is a real legal eagle.

1272
01:34:29.436 --> 01:34:32.815
Hello, Snuggles ? 
Honey, it's me.

1273
01:34:32.940 --> 01:34:36.068
I'm here with Donatella, my friend.

1274
01:34:36.694 --> 01:34:39.697
We're on the boardwalk in Viareggio.

1275
01:34:41.157 --> 01:34:45.661
If she appeals the sentence
will she be able...


1276
01:34:46.954 --> 01:34:48.789
Of course.

1277
01:34:49.039 --> 01:34:52.459
He's sending a driver !
We just have to wait !


1278
01:34:54.962 --> 01:34:57.464
What did you do ?

1279
01:34:57.965 --> 01:35:01.218
What did you do ?

1280
01:35:03.220 --> 01:35:04.722
I'm fine.

1281
01:35:05.598 --> 01:35:07.349
It's okay.

1282
01:35:07.933 --> 01:35:10.227
<i>Let's go sit down...</i>

1283
01:35:10.436 --> 01:35:12.855
get some ice in a cafe...

1284
01:35:12.980 --> 01:35:14.607
You okay ?

1285
01:35:14.732 --> 01:35:18.611
We are, but you're clearly not
with those outfits !


1286
01:35:18.819 --> 01:35:20.487
A <i>cafe...</i>

1287
01:35:24.617 --> 01:35:26.493
Cold beers.

1288
01:35:27.828 --> 01:35:31.624
Naturally, I have some Valium
I stole from my mom.


1289
01:35:31.832 --> 01:35:33.834
2 or 5 mg?

1290
01:35:34.501 --> 01:35:36.378
5 mg!

1291
01:35:38.005 --> 01:35:40.007
A cigarette.

1292
01:35:50.643 --> 01:35:53.896
- Why did I do it?
- You sure are a dummy.


1293
01:35:54.104 --> 01:35:56.273
Luckily, you have a hard head.

1294
01:35:56.482 --> 01:36:00.152
They say I'm too unstable
and they must take my son away.


1295
01:36:00.361 --> 01:36:02.154
They, who ?

1296
01:36:02.613 --> 01:36:05.908
Social services declare
"parental unsuitability".


1297
01:36:07.785 --> 01:36:11.538
Eight of them come to get him,
with police in tow.


1298
01:36:11.664 --> 01:36:13.415
Poor baby's sleeping.

1299
01:36:13.540 --> 01:36:15.793
They don't even let me change him.

1300
01:36:16.001 --> 01:36:19.004
They put him in an institution,
all by himself.


1301
01:36:19.171 --> 01:36:20.881
For a little while.

1302
01:36:21.048 --> 01:36:23.676
They say:
"Just wait, we have to decide."


1303
01:36:24.385 --> 01:36:27.137
- Who ?
- Them.


1304
01:36:27.304 --> 01:36:30.683
So I wait. I cry
every day but I wait.

1305
01:36:30.808 --> 01:36:34.561
They say I cry too much,
and have major depression...


1306
01:36:35.521 --> 01:36:38.315
"if you give him to me
I'll stop crying."


1307
01:36:38.524 --> 01:36:41.151
"No, you have always cried.

1308
01:36:41.318 --> 01:36:43.445
- You cried at school..."
- Me too.


1309
01:36:43.654 --> 01:36:47.700
They know it all: I cried
over homework, over my dad...


1310
01:36:47.825 --> 01:36:49.576
- In the elevator...
- Me too.


1311
01:36:49.702 --> 01:36:51.954
I cried when mom yelled at me
for crying.


1312
01:36:52.162 --> 01:36:53.414
Me too.

1313
01:36:53.580 --> 01:36:57.960
"All right, I have major depression,
so cure me.


1314
01:36:58.168 --> 01:37:01.547
- I was born sad, cure me."
- I was born sad too.


1315
01:37:01.714 --> 01:37:05.426
"Give me Elia. You won't
cure me by taking him away !"


1316
01:37:05.592 --> 01:37:08.721
In fact, kids instill a sense of joy.

1317
01:37:09.221 --> 01:37:12.599
So they say I can go visit him
in the institution.


1318
01:37:13.809 --> 01:37:17.479
And I go there every day, all day.

1319
01:37:17.604 --> 01:37:21.984
I feed him baby food, not meat though,
he only likes apples.


1320
01:37:22.443 --> 01:37:24.737
Elia and I laugh, you know.

1321
01:37:24.862 --> 01:37:27.489
But when I leave, he cries.

1322
01:37:27.698 --> 01:37:29.700
He cries like crazy.

1323
01:37:29.867 --> 01:37:34.330
He grips on to me, they have to
pull him off finger by finger.


1324
01:37:34.496 --> 01:37:38.459
I have to leave him there,
make him think that I want to leave.


1325
01:37:38.959 --> 01:37:41.003
They say I'm not getting better.

1326
01:37:41.879 --> 01:37:45.132
- I want to get better, I do.
- I want to get better too.


1327
01:37:46.967 --> 01:37:49.011
One day they leave us on our own.

1328
01:37:49.219 --> 01:37:53.390
So I take him out in the stroller
to see the Mardi Gras floats.


1329
01:38:02.608 --> 01:38:06.987
What a sight, everyone looks at us,
everyone's smiling.


1330
01:38:07.154 --> 01:38:09.406
"Isn't he cute ?
His name is Elia.


1331
01:38:09.907 --> 01:38:11.909
He's my son, I made him !"

1332
01:38:19.666 --> 01:38:23.545
All of a sudden I see him...
I see him there.


1333
01:38:24.171 --> 01:38:25.672
Him, who ?

1334
01:38:26.298 --> 01:38:27.549
Hi!

1335
01:38:27.758 --> 01:38:30.177
He's there with his real kids.

1336
01:38:32.054 --> 01:38:33.931
- What?
- Want to see him ?


1337
01:38:34.431 --> 01:38:36.058
- Look at him.
- Get lost.


1338
01:38:36.183 --> 01:38:39.186
- Look how cute he is.
- Quit trying to ruin my life.


1339
01:38:39.395 --> 01:38:42.189
- Just look at him.
- Quit trying to ruin my life !


1340
01:38:42.314 --> 01:38:45.067
He says "slut", and other ugly words.

1341
01:38:45.192 --> 01:38:47.152
"You fucked everyone.

1342
01:38:47.319 --> 01:38:49.655
He's not my son,
he's Seven Apples' son."


1343
01:38:49.822 --> 01:38:53.575
What do you want, money ?
Here take this, and this.


1344
01:38:53.951 --> 01:38:56.829
Now get lost
or I'll press charges, okay ?


1345
01:38:57.037 --> 01:38:59.665
- I'll press charges.
- You didn't even look at him !


1346
01:38:59.832 --> 01:39:03.043
I didn't want anything,
I didn't ask him for anything,


1347
01:39:03.210 --> 01:39:06.171
I just wanted to show him
how beautiful Elia was.


1348
01:39:06.338 --> 01:39:07.965
Fuck you !

1349
01:39:10.426 --> 01:39:13.429
I feel like crying but feel ashamed.

1350
01:39:13.595 --> 01:39:16.932
God, I feel so ashamed,
I feel like a fool.


1351
01:39:21.061 --> 01:39:24.857
I can't remember
how to get back to the institution.


1352
01:39:24.982 --> 01:39:27.317
I hop on a random bus.

1353
01:39:31.572 --> 01:39:34.700
Then I get off and walk and walk...

1354
01:39:35.701 --> 01:39:37.703
Fuck you !

1355
01:39:43.876 --> 01:39:46.753
In the meantime, 
Elia falls asleep.

1356
01:39:47.504 --> 01:39:51.633
I think "God, now they're going
to take him away forever."


1357
01:40:08.108 --> 01:40:12.529
I think about how much he'll cry,
how much I'll cry,


1358
01:40:12.738 --> 01:40:15.782
I think about how cruel people can be.

1359
01:40:31.131 --> 01:40:33.509
No more feeling bad all the time,

1360
01:40:33.675 --> 01:40:35.677
no more feeling bad.

1361
01:40:36.637 --> 01:40:39.640
I want to feel good,
we want to feel good.


1362
01:40:41.934 --> 01:40:45.687
We don't want to die,
we want to be together...


1363
01:40:45.938 --> 01:40:47.564
forever.

1364
01:41:28.564 --> 01:41:31.984
Later they call it attempted murder,
attempted suicide.


1365
01:41:32.109 --> 01:41:35.696
Words like that,
what ridiculous words.


1366
01:41:35.862 --> 01:41:38.240
But they don't understand a thing.

1367
01:41:40.617 --> 01:41:43.954
While we sink down, we are happy.

1368
01:41:45.747 --> 01:41:48.458
Luckily they rescued you.

1369
01:41:54.089 --> 01:41:56.758
We're so tired, the two of us.

1370
01:42:00.512 --> 01:42:03.265
We should get some rest.

1371
01:42:05.017 --> 01:42:07.102
I'd like to sleep for a month.

1372
01:42:07.269 --> 01:42:09.521
I'd say a year.

1373
01:42:12.149 --> 01:42:14.234
<i>Or even die...</i>

1374
01:42:17.738 --> 01:42:21.992
So my mom would finally be happy,
everybody would be.


1375
01:42:22.618 --> 01:42:24.411
Are you crazy ?

1376
01:42:26.788 --> 01:42:29.041
And what would I do ?

1377
01:42:31.877 --> 01:42:34.796
- You ?
- Good thing I have you.


1378
01:42:35.547 --> 01:42:37.674
- Me?
'You!


1379
01:42:37.799 --> 01:42:39.885
- You !
- Good thing you have me.


1380
01:42:40.052 --> 01:42:41.053
You !

1381
01:42:57.819 --> 01:43:00.656
Jesus, Beatrice, move it !

1382
01:43:07.829 --> 01:43:09.956
God, there they are !

1383
01:43:11.583 --> 01:43:13.293
Beatrice ?

1384
01:43:14.044 --> 01:43:16.797
Where's Donatella ?
Search the area.


1385
01:43:22.678 --> 01:43:26.807
You can both come back to Villa Biondi
with a new therapeutic plan.


1386
01:43:26.932 --> 01:43:29.559
I spoke to the judge,

1387
01:43:29.726 --> 01:43:32.604
no judicial psych hospital, no jail,
but no more mischief I


1388
01:43:34.481 --> 01:43:37.484
Listen to me, where is Donatella ?

1389
01:44:06.596 --> 01:44:07.973
Sorry.

1390
01:44:13.395 --> 01:44:16.273
Don't move her,
she banged her head !


1391
01:44:16.523 --> 01:44:18.650
- Call an ambulance.
- Hold on.


1392
01:44:19.609 --> 01:44:22.279
- How are you ?
- No ambulance.


1393
01:44:22.487 --> 01:44:25.031
You don't look before crossing ?!

1394
01:44:27.033 --> 01:44:30.412
- Don't move.
- Take it easy.


1395
01:44:31.037 --> 01:44:34.040
- Don't move.
- No ambulance.


1396
01:44:37.794 --> 01:44:39.755
- Any news ?
- An accident.


1397
01:44:39.921 --> 01:44:41.673
A lady walked into traffic.

1398
01:44:43.300 --> 01:44:45.510
Beatrice, get in the car.

1399
01:44:45.677 --> 01:44:47.262
Giancarlo, help her.

1400
01:44:48.805 --> 01:44:51.057
The ambulance is on its way.

1401
01:44:52.267 --> 01:44:55.437
Give her some space, all right.

1402
01:44:56.563 --> 01:44:59.274
- Isn't there another lady ?
- Right here.


1403
01:45:00.776 --> 01:45:02.819
She had a pink dress on.

1404
01:45:03.028 --> 01:45:06.281
The lady in the pink dress
who was right here...


1405
01:45:06.823 --> 01:45:09.159
where'd she go ? 
She was just here.

1406
01:45:19.169 --> 01:45:22.088
What a night, we had a blast.

1407
01:46:22.482 --> 01:46:24.484
- Hi.
- Hi.


1408
01:46:28.280 --> 01:46:29.656
How are you doing ?

1409
01:46:30.407 --> 01:46:32.409
<i>Uh... normal.</i>

1410
01:46:34.870 --> 01:46:37.038
<i>Normal...</i>

1411
01:46:37.622 --> 01:46:40.667
Well, you look pretty good for normal.

1412
01:46:45.672 --> 01:46:47.674
Do you know who I am ?

1413
01:46:48.550 --> 01:46:51.303
The lady who was hiding in the plants.

1414
01:46:56.057 --> 01:46:59.185
- You know when your back tingles ?
- Yeah...


1415
01:47:00.312 --> 01:47:03.189
That's me tickling you.

1416
01:47:04.274 --> 01:47:06.192
It tickles at night.

1417
01:47:08.069 --> 01:47:11.406
That means I think about you
even more at night.


1418
01:47:15.035 --> 01:47:17.579
I have sand in my bathing suit.

1419
01:47:23.209 --> 01:47:26.463
Hey you,
come in, it's not that cold !


1420
01:47:59.704 --> 01:48:01.247
You're great !

1421
01:48:29.275 --> 01:48:30.735
Where'll you go now ?

1422
01:48:31.653 --> 01:48:33.863
I don't know.

1423
01:48:34.030 --> 01:48:37.367
I'll go somewhere to get better,
so one day...


1424
01:48:39.619 --> 01:48:41.997
we'll be able to meet again.

1425
01:48:45.417 --> 01:48:49.295
I'm happy, you have a lovely family.

1426
01:48:58.013 --> 01:49:01.182
Elia, come play volleyball.

1427
01:49:01.307 --> 01:49:04.769
- What a drag, I'm so short.
- No you're not.


1428
01:49:06.438 --> 01:49:10.191
I'll come play on
Luca and Tommaso's team !


1429
01:49:12.152 --> 01:49:14.529
We're just late bloomers...

1430
01:49:18.324 --> 01:49:20.785
Giulia, do a good serve !

1431
01:49:22.579 --> 01:49:24.330
Serve strong !

1432
01:49:42.098 --> 01:49:44.809
Guys, zero to one in our favor!

1433
01:49:47.228 --> 01:49:49.230
Good job !

1434
01:52:07.118 --> 01:52:11.998
LIKE CRAZY